overview.en: GCT is a public chain based on the consensus mechanism of DDPOS. In the future, it will build a blockchain ecosystem covering the global gold light luxury goods trading platform, the mining union digital exchange and the mining union digital bank.
overview.zh: GCT是一条基于DDPOS共识机制的公有链，未来将打造涵盖全球黄金轻奢品交易平台和矿业联盟数字交易所和矿业联盟数字银行的区块链全领域生态
